HEADWORD: equalitarianism
<hw>equalitarianism</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>the doctrine of the equality
of mankind and the desirability of political and economic and social
equality.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> egalitarianism.</syn>⟦br⟧
